Bill Whi pp le —and oh, he was the best cre tur ! —I most wish ’t it had
been me, I do.”

“My George ! It’s the beat en est thing I ever struck. And then what did
you all do?”

“Well, we hollered and took on, but it’s so wide there we couldn’t
