I didn’t wait for no breakfa st —I warn’t hungr y.”

“O ld man,” said the young one, “I reckon we might double- te am it
together ; what do you think ?”

“I ain’t un dispo sed. What’s your lin e— main ly?”

“ J our prin ter by trade ; do a little in pat ent medi cin es;
