Well, the old man he liked that speech, and he mighty soon got it so
he could do it first- rat e. It seemed like he was just born for it; and
when he had his hand in and was excited, it was perfectly lovely the
way he would rip and tear and ra ir up behind when he was getting it off.

The first chance we got the duke he had some show - bills prin ted; and
