with their heads bo bbing and sk im ming along, away up there under the
t ent - roof, and every lady’s ro se- le af y dress fla pping soft and sil ky
around her hi ps, and she looking like the most lo ve liest par as ol .

And then faster and faster they went, all of them d anc ing, first
one foot out in the air and then the other, the horses leaning more
and more, and the ringmaster going round and round the cen ter po le,
crac king his whip and shouting “H i !— hi !” and the cl own crac king jo kes
behind him; and by and by all hands dropped the re ins, and every lady
