I ever see, and then sca m per ed out, and everybody clapped their hands
and went just about wil d.

Well, all through the circus they done the most astonish ing things;
and all the time that cl own carried on so it most killed the people.
The ringmaster couldn’t ever say a word to him but he was back at him
