pi le — twenty ele g ant little pi les. Everybody looked hungry at it, and
li cked their ch op s. Then they ra ked it into the bag again, and I see
the king begin to s well himself up for another speech. He says:

“ Fri en ds all, my poor brother that lays yonder has done generous by
them that’s left behind in the va le of sor r ers. He has done generous
by these yer poor little lam bs that he loved and shel ter ed, and that’s
left father less and mother less. Yes, and we that knowed him knows that
