“ — they bein’ parti ck ler friends o’ the disea sed. That’s why they’re
inv ited here this even in ’; but to-morrow we want all to
com e— everybody; for he respe cted everybod y, he liked everybod y, and
so it’s fitten that his funeral orgies sh ’d be public .”

And so he went a- mo oning on and on, li king to hear himself talk, and
every little while he fetched in his funeral orgies again, till the
