rea ds it and put s it in his pocket, and says:

“P o or William, aff lic ted as he is, his hear t’s al uz right. A s ks me
to inv ite everybody to come to the funer al — wants me to make ’em all
wel come. But he needn’t ’a’ wor ri ed— it was jest what I was at.”

Then he wea ves along again, perfectly ca ’m, and goes to dropping in
