the Gre ek or go, outside, open, ab road ; and the He bre w je es um, to
plan t, cover up; hence inter . So, you see, funeral orgies is an open
er public funer al.”

He was the worst I ever struck. Well, the ir on- jaw ed man he laughed
right in his face. Everybody was sho ck ed. Everybody says, “Why,
