“Why, Robin son, hain’t you heard the new s? This is Harvey Wilk s.”

The king he smiled eag er, and shoved out his fla pp er, and says:

“Is it my poor brother ’s dear good friend and physi ci an ? I —”

“Keep your hands off me!” says the do ctor. “You talk like an
