“All right, doctor ,” says the king, kinder mo cking him; “ we’ll try and
get ’em to send for you ; ” which made them all laugh , and they said it
was a pri me good hi t.




CHAPTER XX VI


Well, when they was all gone the king he as ks Mary Jane how they was
