“What — regul ar ?”

“Yes — regul ar. His pew ’s right over oppos ite our n — on t’other side the
pul p it.”

“I thought he lived in London ?”

“Well, he do es. Where would he live ?”

“But I thought you lived in Sheffiel d?”

I see I was up a stum p. I had to let on to get choked with a
