“Why, who ’s that?”

“Who do you reckon ’ti s?”

“I hain’t no idea. Who is it?”

“It’s Tom Sawyer !”

By jings, I most sl um ped through the floor ! But there warn’t no time
to swa p kni v es; the old man grabbed me by the hand and shoo k, and kept
