and cr y; and then how they both did fire off questions about Sid, and
Mary, and the rest of the tri be.

But if they was joy ful, it warn’t nothing to what I was; for it was
like being born again, I was so glad to find out who I was. Well, they
fro ze to me for two hour s; and at last, when my chin was so tired it
