“Well, Sally, I’m in fault, and I ac knowledge it; I’ve been re mis s;
but I won’t let to-morrow go by without stopping up them hole s.”

“Oh, I wouldn’t hurry; next year ’ll do. M ati l da Angel in a A ra min t a
Phelp s!”

