That was just his way. If it didn’t suit him to explain a thing to
you, he wouldn’t do it. You might p ump at him a week, it wouldn’t make
no difference.

He’d got all that coat- of - arms business fix ed, so now he started in to
fin ish up the rest of that part of the work, which was to plan out a
