“It was in the early ’ 6 0 ’s at the di gg ings. I was a young chap then,
ho t- bloo ded and reck less, ready to turn my hand at any thing; I got
among bad companion s, took to drink, had no luck with my claim , took to
the bus h, and in a word became what you would call over here a high way
